item.title: Tele Help!
item.dc:creator: @_Sunkist _Sunkist_
item.description:
@_Sunkist wrote:

go under client and search for

else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("mb"))

you should see something like this

else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("mb")) { if(teleblock == true){ sendMessage("A magical force stops you from teleporting."); //made by Musicmad441 } else { teleportToX = xxxx; teleportToY = yyyy; sendMessage("You teleport to the mage arena"); } }

where it says teleporttox = xxxx and teleporttoy = yyyy

put the new co-ords you want in place of “xxxx” and “yyyy”
